        <p data-uuid="1dbf1be1d8b7472d9329113ec0b33df9">More than 100 innocent slaves who were not part of Turner’s group were killed in an attempt to stop the rebellion. Turner himself led authorities on a chase around the countryside for six weeks. He hid in caves and in the woods before he was caught and brought to trial.&#160;</p>
